    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="transcript" id="J237">
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>I think just how my shape will rise --</l>
                    <l>When I shall be "forgiven" --</l>
                    <l>Till Hair -- and Eyes -- and timid Head --</l>
                    <l>Are out of sight -- in Heaven --</l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>I think just how my lips will weigh --</l>
                    <l>With shapeless -- quivering -- prayer --</l>
                    <l>That you -- so late -- "Consider" me --</l>
                    <l>The "Sparrow" of your Care --</l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>I mind me that of Anguish -- sent --</l>
                    <l>Some drifts were moved away --</l>
                    <l>Before my simple bosom -- broke --</l>
                    <l>And why not this -- if they?</l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>And so I con that thing -- "forgiven" --</l>
                    <l>Until -- delirious -- borne --</l>
                    <l>By my long bright -- and longer -- trust --</l>
                    <l>I drop my Heart -- unshriven!</l>
                </lg>

            </div>     
        </body>
